  <brief_title>Patient Understanding (Cognitive Debriefing) of a Daily Diary of Gastroparesis Symptoms</brief_title>
  <official_title>Protocol for the Patient Understanding (Cognitive Debriefing) of a Modified Gastroparesis Cardinal Symptom Index (GCSI) Daily Diary</official_title>
